	<div class="container">
		<div class="project-hero__content">
			
			<h1 class="project-hero__title">For families across California, a desperate struggle to get mental health care</h1>

			
						<p class="project-hero__intro">Californians with mental illness—and their family members—describe pleading with insurance providers for the treatment they need.</p>
			
							<div class="project-hero__caption">

											<svg role="img" class="icon icon--camera" aria-label="camera"><use xlink:href="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/themes/thenewsproject/dist/svg/dist/symbol/svg/sprite.symbol.svg#camera"></use></svg>						<span>In her daughter&#039;s room, Seong Brown adjusts rose petals atop the clothing she wore when she died. 
</span>
									</div>
					</div>
	</div>
