		<div class="project-series-footer__info">
						<h2 class="project-series-footer__title">Breakdown: Mental health in California</h2>
			
						<div class="project-series-footer__author">
				<a href="https://calmatters.org/author/jocelyn-wiener/">
				<img alt='Jocelyn Wiener' src='https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/Wiener_Jocelyn-e1581014107366-96x96.jpg' class='avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' />				</a>

				<div>
										<span class="project-series-footer__author-byline">
						By <a href="https://calmatters.org/author/jocelyn-wiener/">Jocelyn Wiener</a>
					</span>
					
					
					<ul class="project-series-footer__author-social">
